Within-Run Predicted vs. True Time Series

All data within run (263 TRs) were used to fit the model. Predicted timeseries are shown for each run.

The predicted timeseries uses a design matrix that was convolved with the hrf, while true values are fit to scaled timeseries (median of motor region voxels).

Green colors represent when the task came.
